## TIER 3: When NOT to Publish

STOP and reconsider if:

- [ ] Page is under 100 lines (tool pages) or 200 lines (guides)
- [ ] No clear search query being targeted
- [ ] Content is mostly template sections (How to Use + FAQ + Related)
- [ ] Just duplicating official documentation without adding unique value
- [ ] No code examples, tables, or practical guidance
- [ ] Another page already covers this topic adequately
- [ ] You can't articulate why someone would choose this over Google result #1

**When in doubt, don't publish. Expand an existing page instead.**

