## TIER 4: SEO Technical Requirements

### Title and Meta

- `seo_title`: Under 60 characters, includes primary keyword
- `seo_description`: Under 155 characters, includes value proposition + keyword
- H1 must closely match the primary search query
- Slug format: `ai-{descriptive-slug}` (e.g., `ai-openai-429-errors`)

### Internal Linking

- Every page links OUT to 3-5 related tools/guides
- Every NEW page must be linked FROM at least 2 existing pages
- Use descriptive anchor text (not "click here" or "learn more")
- Example: "See [OpenAI Rate Limits by Tier](/ai-openai-rate-limits)" (good)

### URL Strategy

- All tool pages use `ai-` prefix for brand consistency
- Keep slugs short but descriptive
- Use hyphens, not underscores
- No dates in URLs (content should be evergreen)

