## TIER 5: Content Freshness

### When to Update Existing Content

Update content when:

- New models are released (quarterly check)
- Pricing changes (update `data/pricing.json` AND relevant guide pages)
- Rate limit structures change
- Error patterns change

### Freshness Checklist (Run Quarterly)

- [ ] Are model names current? (no deprecated models like gpt-3.5-turbo-0301)
- [ ] Are pricing numbers accurate?
- [ ] Are rate limit tables current?
- [ ] Do code examples use current API patterns?

**Note:** This is a manual check, not an automated system. Run it when you remember or when major model releases happen.

